msgid "Kiten"
msgstr "Kiten"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kiten.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Japanese Reference and Study Tool"
msgstr "Instrumento de Referentia e Studio de Japonese"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kiten.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"Kiten is a Japanese reference and study tool. It features an English to "
"Japanese and Japanese to English dictionary, as well as a Kanji dictionary. "
"For the Kanji dictionary there are multiple ways supported to look up "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Kiten es un instrumento de referentia e studio japonese. Illo include un "
"dictionario anglese-japonese e japonese-anglese, assi como un dictionario "
"de kanji. Pro le dictionario de kanji, existe multiple methodos supportate "
"pro cercar characteres."

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
